{"tid":595944,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴有意購入華拉尼 與拜利打做成未來最強中堅組合","createTime":"2018-03-17T07:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T08:48:31.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9dc131fe9e4b91f99239be99b7d22ef60425833","tid":595944,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里中堅華拉尼受到曼聯垂青，這支英超勁旅有意把這位法國國腳帶去英超聯賽。<br />\n<br />\n華拉尼在2011年加盟皇馬，今季受到施丹重用，上陣時間不少。<br />\n<br />\n然而，摩連奴有興趣把這位法國國腳帶去英超，華拉尼也承認確有此事。<br />\n<br />\n「不是直接找我，但是的確有些接觸，間接的接觸。」華拉尼說道。"},{"pid":"831d508c2380dae7e383a554267f18eb08e5ecbe","tid":595944,"uid":7729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"今季廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d87873ecf7f6fb2d135fd40f8360558a6fa4cb1","tid":595944,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"831d508c2380dae7e383a554267f18eb08e5ecbe","tid":595944,"uid":7729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"今季廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"華拉尼泊大巴有豐富經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3dd44dda31492b3142312d8a4516b17d92a124","tid":595944,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"唔差在推鍾斯 同smalling上去踢防中啦"},{"pid":"c5a89996fa60650e89abc8fae2fd0be75c940d90","tid":595944,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔放迪基亞<br />\n<br />\n點係皇到買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f567492b57625fdcd341b702458abe3ee00d06d","tid":595944,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"又買二線<br />\ndaddy 節儉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc45173a93e65a7c38ea2